Englande, and before Duchesse of Britayne, doughter to the Kyng of
Nauer, &amp; wife to kyng Henry the iiij. died at the mannor of Haueryng,
and was buried by her husbande at Canterbury, in whiche tyme disceased
the Countesse of Warwicke, and Henry Archebishop of Yorke.
               
