with Carpettes and Tapissery:The Courte at the Blacke Friers. on the right hande of the court was
hanged a clothe of estate, with a Chayer and Cusshions of riche Tissue,
for the kyng, and on the left hande of the Courte, was set riche chayer
for the Quene. When the place was redy, the Kyng and the Quene wer
ascited by Docter Sampson, to appere before the Legates, at the forenamed
