cōueyed from Cawod to Sheffelde castle and there deliuered to therle
of Shrewsburies kepyng till the kynges pleasure were knowen: Of
this attachement was muche commonyng amongest the common people,
wherfore many were glad, for surely he was not in the fauor of the
cominaltie.
