in themperours Cowrte at Gaunte: My Lorde Ambassador
of Englande, I meruayle not a lytell why the Kyng your Master dalyeth
so with themperours Aunte, she is dissended I assure you of a noble
bloode and hye Parentage, themperours Maiestie may not nor wyl
not suffre so
