               In the name of God Amen, I Wyllyam Tracy of Todyngton in y•
countie of Gloucester esquier make my Testament &amp; last wille as hereafter
foloweth. Fyrst and before al other thinges I commit me vnto
God and to his mercy, beleuyng without any doubt or mistrust that by
his grace and the merites of Iesus Christ, &amp; by the vertue of his passion
and of his resurreccion I haue and shal haue remission of my sinnes
and resurreccion of body and soule according as it is written,Iob. 
